er: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Overlooked Mastermind<br>Source Inner Sea Races pg. 212<br>Some half-orcs use half-orcs’ brutish stereotypes to their advantage, causing others to underestimate their intelligence and scheming. Such half-orcs gain a +2 racial bonus on Bluff, Diplomacy, and Sense Motive checks. This bonus increases to +4 against other humanoids. They also receive a +2 racial bonus on Bluff checks to feign ignorance and Sense Motive checks to intercept secret messages, and this stacks with the above bonus. This racial trait replaces intimidating, orc ferocity, and weapon familiarity.<br></div></div></div><br><div align="center"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">此种族特性替换武器熟悉、威慑力</span></span></strong></div><br><span style="color: #00C080;" class="bbc_color"><strong>萨满加持（Shaman Enhancement）</strong></span> <span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">PFS禁用</span><br><strong>出自《第一世界遗产 pg. 5》</strong><br>某些半兽人懂得能够增强盟友的力量与残暴的仪式。此半兽人在法术辨识获得+2种族加值。除外，当这个半兽人获得动物伙伴、联结坐骑、部属、魔宠或魂兽时，该生物在力量、敏捷或体质获得+2加值，由半兽人决定。此种族特性替换武器熟悉和威慑力。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Shaman Enhancement<br>Source Legacy of the First World pg. 5<br>Certain half-orcs know rituals to enhance the strength and brutality of their allies. These half-orcs gain a +2 racial bonus on Spellcraft checks. In addition, when such a half-orc acquires an animal companion, bonded mount, cohort, familiar, or spirit animal, that creature gains a +2 bonus to Strength, Dexterity, or Constitution, as selected by the half-orc. This racial trait replaces weapon familiarity and intimidating.<br></div></div></div><br><div align="center"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">此种族特性替换兽人凶猛</span></span></strong></div><br><span style="color: #00C080;" class="bbc_color"><strong>敏锐黑暗视觉（Acute Darkvision）</strong></span><br><strong>出自《进阶种族手册 pg. 1》</strong><br>有些半兽人拥有异常敏锐的黑暗视觉，他们获得黑暗视觉90尺。此种族特性取代兽人凶猛。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Acute Darkvision<br>Source Advanced Race Guide pg. 1<br>Some half-orcs have exceptionally sharp darkvision, gaining darkvision 90 feet. This racial trait replaces orc ferocity.<br></div></div></div><br><span style="color: #00C080;" class="bbc_color"><strong>兽王（Beastmaster）</strong></span><br><strong>出自《进阶种族手册 pg. 1》，《进阶玩家手册 pg. 1》</strong><br>有些半兽人跟空想的野兽有种精神上的亲切感，会去捕捉牠们或跟牠们一同生活和狩猎。拥有此种族特性的半兽人将鞭子（whips）与捕网（nets）视为军用武器，并在驯养动物检定获得+2种族加值。此种族特性取代兽人凶猛。<br><div