瞳孔也没什么特别的，但其他类人生物对此心神不安。非精灵的类人生物在对抗此精灵施放的造成困惑或恐惧的法术时豁免检定承受-1罚值。此外，拥有此种族特性的精灵在挫败士气的威吓检定获得+2种族加值。此种族特性取代精灵魔法。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Creepy<br>Source Horror Adventures pg. 38<br>For some elves, their long, slender limbs and large pupils evoke not attraction, but unease in other humanoids. Non-elf humanoids take a –1 penalty on saving throws against spells these elves cast that cause confusion or fear. In addition, elves with this trait gain a +2 racial bonus on Intimidate checks to demoralize. This racial trait replaces elven magic.<br></div></div></div><br><span style="color: #8000FF;" class="bbc_color"><strong>沙漠跑者（Desert Runner）</strong></span><br><strong>出自《Advanced Race Guide pg. 22, Advanced Player&#039;s Guide pg. 12》</strong><br>部分精灵在沙漠的深处发迹，永远漫游在燃烧般灼热的土地之上。拥有此种族特性的精灵在避免疲乏、力竭、或奔跑、急行军、饥饿、口渴、炎热或寒冷环境造成的不良效果时，体质检定和强韧豁免获得+4种族加值。此种族特性取代精灵魔法。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('d