技巧（Woodcraft）</strong></span><br><strong>出自《Advanced Race Guide pg. 23, Advanced Player&#039;s Guide pg. 13》</strong><br>没有人能比精灵更深入了解荒野，尤其是关于森林的秘密。拥有此种族特性的精灵在知识［自然］和生存检定获得+1种族加值。在森林地形中，此加值提升至+2。此种族特性取代精灵魔法。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Woodcraft<br>Source Advanced Race Guide pg. 23, Advanced Player&#039;s Guide pg. 13<br>Elves know the deep secrets of the wild like no others, especially secrets of the forests. Elves with this racial trait gain a +1 racial bonus on Knowledge (nature) and Survival checks. In forest terrain, these bonuses improve to +2. This racial trait replaces elven magic.<br></div></div></div><br><div align="center"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">此种族特性替换精灵魔法，敏锐感官</span></span></strong></div><br><span style="color: #8000FF;" class="bbc_color"><strong>恒心（Ageless Patience）</strong></span><br><strong>出自《Inner Sea Races pg. 210》</strong><br>有些精灵家庭受到严格光荣的非精灵文化的强烈影响，例如在塔尔多等国家成长的Forlorn精灵，以及被明族人旅行者影响的精瑛（Jinin）精灵。这种态度结合精灵的长寿，誔生出特别耐心的精灵，他们在无时间限制的情况下做出更好的结果。这些精灵在技能检定中取20时获得+2种族加值。此种族特性替换精灵魔法和敏锐感官。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" styl