 else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Natural Swimmer<br>Source Pathfinder #124: City in the Deep pg. 79<br>Mordant Spire elves learn to dive and swim at an early age. Elves with this trait gain a +2 racial bonus on Swim checks and can always take 10 on a Swim check, even if distracted or endangered when swimming. This racial trait replaces elven magic and keen senses.<br></div></div></div><br><span style="color: #8000FF;" class="bbc_color"><strong>索维瑞安精灵（Sovyrian-Born）</strong></span><br><strong>出自《Inner Sea Races pg. 211》</strong><br>来自上古精灵文明——索维瑞安（Sovyrian）的精灵比大多数文明浸泡在更为悠久的知识中。他们在知识［历史］、知识［地方］、和法术辨识检定获得+2种族加值。此种族特性替换精灵魔法和敏锐感官。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Sovyrian-Born<br>Source Inner Sea Races pg. 211<br>Elves who come from the ancient elven civilization of Sovyrian are steeped in lore older than most civilizations. They gain a +2 racial bonus on Knowledge (history), Knowledge (local), and Spellcraft checks. This racial trait replaces elven magic and keen senses.<br></div></div></div><br><div al