<h5 id="subject_1017900">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=107183.msg1017900#msg1017900" rel="nofollow">缺陷（Drawback）——来些比较轻量的缺陷让你的角色更加生动</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1017900'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1017900'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #10 于:</strong> 2019-10-19, 周六 19:18:04 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_1017900_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
</div>
