<div class="inner" id="msg_1017900"><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>重要说明</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">【Champions of Corruption】的三个缺陷（Drawback）——污秽烙印（Foul Brand），揭露之影（Umbral Unmasking），违反自然（Warded Against Nature）我猜是邪恶角色限定，本身的栅目「Wicked and Weird」本意是指邪恶的家伙迟早会露出马脚，相由心生，拥抱黑暗的人会从他的外官反映出来。当然他们也接受如此并有些会加以展示来换取力量（差不多的意思），所以大概是他人能从这些缺陷看穿邪恶角色的本质</div></div></div><br>忧虑（Anxious）　　［缺陷］：你在孩提时代由于没能守口如瓶而遭受了痛苦，比如你不小心将自己的家人暴露给了敌方的审讯者，你从此以后说话都变得小心翼翼。你的交涉检定承受-2罚值，并由于斟酌言辞而必须缓慢说话。除非另有说明，你一般不能以超过悄悄话的音量说话。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Anxious [Link]<br>Source Quests and Campaigns pg. 22<br>After suffering terribly for not being tightlipped enough as a child, such as when you accidentally exposed your family to enemy inquisitors, you developed a habit of being overly cautious with your words. You take a –2 penalty on Diplomacy checks and must speak slowly due to the concentration required. Unless stated otherwise, you are assumed to not be speaking at a volume above a whisper.</div></div></div><br>依存症（Attached）　　［缺陷］：你有强烈的情感依存，你非常害怕失去某人或某物。由DM选择一项你的依存物件。每当你的依存对像受到威胁、陷入危险或被别人占有，你的意志豁免承受-1罚值，对抗恐惧效果的豁免承受-2罚值。若你依存的人或物体丢失、死亡或被摧毁，此缺陷被替换为疑虑（Doubt）。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Attached [Link]<br>Source Ultimate Campaign pg. 64<br>You have a strong emotional attachment to a person or object that you’re terrif ied of losing. The GM chooses the object of your attachment. Whenever the object of your attachment is either threatened, in danger, or in someone else’s possession, you take a –1 penalty on Will saves and a –2 penalty on saves against fear effects. If the person or object to which you’re attached is ever lost, killed, or destroyed, exchange this drawback for the Doubt drawback.</div></div></div><br>贪婪（Avarice）　　［缺陷］：你被根深蒂固的强烈贪婪所驱使。每当分配财宝货币时，你必须获得比同伴更多的份额，否则你就会陷入深深的嫉妒和虐待倾向之中。当财宝分配结束，而你没能获得比其他任何人多出至少10%的份额，你会变得不愿帮助你的队友。你性格变得暴躁，并且在接下来1周内不能使用援护他人（aid another）行动。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Avarice [Link]<br>Source Ultimate Campaign pg. 65<br>Deep, compulsive greed gnaws at you. Whenever monetary treasure is divided, you must end up with a greater share of that treasure than your companions or you’re wracked with feelings of jealousy and ill will. When treasure is divided, if you do not end up with at least 10% more treasure than any other individual companion does, you have a hard time being helpful to your allies. You become irritable, and can’t take the aid another action for the next week.</div></div></div><br>被背叛（Betrayed）<sup>Spymaster&#039;s Handbook</sup>　　［缺陷］：有人向危险的权威组织——例如伽尔特的灰花匠（Gray Gardeners of Galt）、切利亚斯的高阶审判者、或马扎利的芒里萨议会（Council of Mwanyisa of Mzali）举报了你，而你勉强地死里逃生。你事后不断猜疑你的直觉，让你不确定是否去再相信他人，如果你再次遇到那组织的特工，那就太危险了。你在评估气氛（get hunches）的察言观色检定双投取低，并且即使你有其它能力在正常情况下能使你重投此检定，你也不能重投。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Betrayed [Link]<br>Source Spymaster&#039;s Handbook pg. 6<br>You were reported to a dangerous authority such as the Gray Gardeners of Galt, the high inquisitors of Cheliax, or the Council of Mwanyisa of Mzali, and narrowly escaped death. You second-guess your instincts constantly, leaving you never sure whether or not to trust someone and endangered if you encounter that group’s agents again.&nbsp; You can roll twice and take the lower result on Sense Motive checks to get hunches. You cannot reroll this result, even if you have another ability that would normally allow you to do so.</div></div></div><br>苦涩经历（Bitter）<sup>Antihero&#039;s Handbook</sup>　　［缺陷］：你被那些你信任的家伙反复伤害过，这使你变得难以接受帮助。当你从盟友的业职特性、法术或类法术能力获得治疗时，治疗量-1hp。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Bitter [Link]<br>Source Antihero&#039;s Handbook pg. 6<br>You have been hurt repeatedly by those you trusted, and it has become difficult for you to accept help. When you receive healing from an ally’s class feature, spell, or spell-like ability, reduce the amount of that healing by 1 hit point.</div></div></div><br>盛气凌人（Condescending）　　［缺陷］：你在成长中充满自信，觉得只有那些与你相近的人才值得尊重。你以一种相当恶劣的态度对待那些与你不同种族、民族或国籍的人。你在试图提高目标生物对你的态度等级时，交涉和威吓检定承受-5罚值。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Condescending [Link]<br>Source Quests and Campaigns pg. 22<br>Raised with the assurance that only those like you are truly worthy of respect, you have an offputting way of demonstrating that you look down on those not of your race and ethnicity or nationality. You take a –5 penalty on Diplomacy and Intimidate checks to improve other creatures’ attitudes toward you.</div></div></div><br>嗜虐（Cruelty）　　［缺陷］：你从小就热爱将对手身心都彻底打垮并以之为荣，你发现你特别喜欢将敌人的脸整个踩进泥巴里去。每当你参加战斗时，如果30英尺内有陷入濒死或无助的敌人，你对其他并未陷入濒死或无助的敌人的攻击骰承受-2罚值。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Cruelty [Link]<br>Source Quests and Campaigns pg. 22<br>You were rewarded as a child for flaunting your victory over others as completely as possible, and you discovered you enjoyed the feeling of rubbing your foes’ faces in the dirt. Whenever you are engaged in combat and there are dying or helpless foes within 30 feet, you take a –2 penalty on attack rolls against foes who are neither dying nor helpless.</div></div></div><br>依赖（Dependent）　　［缺陷］：你总是过度在意别人对你的认同。每当你的交涉检定失败，你变得战栗1小时。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Dependent [Link]<br>Source Ultimate Campaign pg. 65<br>You are dependent upon the acceptance of others. Whenever you fail a Diplomacy check, you become shaken for 1 hour.</div></div></div><br>空白面具（Empty Mask）<sup>Spymaster&#039;s Handbook</sup>　　［缺陷］：您花费很长的时间隐藏自己的真实身份以逃避你的政治敌人，以至你失去了太多的自我。你在对抗胁迫子学派的意志豁免检定承受-1罚值。若对抗知道你的真实身份的敌人时此罚值提升至-2。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Empty Mask [Link]<br>Source Spymaster&#039;s Handbook pg. 7<br>You have spent so long hiding your true identity to escape political enemies that you have lost much of your sense of self. You take a -1 penalty on Will saving throws against compulsions. This penalty increases to -2 against foes who know your true identity.</div></div></div><br>恐虫（Entomophobe）<sup>Antihero&#039;s Handbook</sup>　　［缺陷］：你年幼时跟虫类有个惨痛的经历使您深深地对种种害虫恐惧，特别是当它们汇聚成集群时。你对抗虫类时攻击承受-2罚值，而你在对抗产生反胃状态的集群的扰乱心神能力时豁免检定承受-2罚值。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Entomophobe [Link]<br>Source Antihero&#039;s Handbook pg. 6<br>A harrowing experience with insects when you were young instilled in you a deep-seated fear of vermin of all description, especially when they swarm together. You take a –2 penalty on attacks against vermin, and you take a –2 penalty on saving throws against the nauseated condition of a swarm’s distraction ability.</div></div></div><br>顾家（Family Ties）　　［缺陷］：你的家人是你的一切，当你不能回应他们的期待时你会变得消沉不已。当一个家庭成员对你提出一个要求，如果你没能通过一个DC 20的意志豁免检定，你必须履行此请求，否则你的所有基于感知和魅力的属性检定和技能检定承受-2罚值，直到你完成要求为止。你可以在每天开始时重掷该意志豁免。若你没有家人，不能选择该缺陷。若你失去家人或与他们失去联系，此缺陷被替换为疑虑（Doubt）。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Family Ties [Link]<br>Source Ultimate Campaign pg. 65<br>Your family is extremely important to you, and you feel disheartened when you can’t do what they ask. When a family member makes a request of you, you must fulf ill that request or take a –2 penalty on all Wisdom- and Charisma-based ability checks and skill checks until you either do what was requested or succeed at a DC 20 Will saving throw, which you can attempt once per day at the start of each day. You can’t take this drawback if you have no family. If you ever lose your family or lose contact with your family, exchange this drawback for the Doubt drawback.</div></div></div><br>污秽烙印（Foul Brand）<sup>Champions of Corruption</sup>　　［缺陷］：你的血肉上烙有一个邪恶神祇的印记。若此印记在你的手，你在解除装置、易容和巧手检定承受-1罚值。若此记在你的脸，你在唬骗、交涉和易容检定承受-2罚值。此烙印在施法时不视为法器。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Foul Brand [Link]<br>Source Champions of Corruption pg. 29<br>You have the symbol of an evil deity burned into your flesh. If the symbol is on your hand, you take a –1 penalty on Disable Device, Disguise, and Sleight of Hand checks. If the symbol is on your face, you take a –2 penalty on Bluff, Diplomacy, and Disguise checks. This does not count as a holy symbol for the purposes of a divine focus for spellcasting.</div></div></div><br>愧于诈骗（Guilty Fraud）<sup>Spymaster&#039;s Handbook</sup>　　［缺陷］：你透过诡计获得你不配拥有的事物，而你对于此劣迹的内疚感使你对四周的环境分神。你对起始态度为冷漠或以上的生物的唬骗检定承受-4罚值。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.d