<br>Source Antihero&#039;s Handbook pg. 6<br>You have become so accustomed to binging on the finer things in life that you find going without such excess particularly strenuous. Goods and services cost you 10% more (and can’t be paid for by allies), and you need twice as much food and liquid as normal for the purposes of preventing starvation and thirst (Pathfinder RPG Core Rulebook 444).</div></div></div><br>魔法笨蛋（Magical Klutz）<sup>Spymaster&#039;s Handbook</sup>　　［缺陷］：你出生在过多魔法被怪异扭曲之地，例如盖布（Geb）、法力废墟（Mana Wastes）、或奈克斯（Nex），而魔法在你的身边危险地化为实际干扰。你在盲目启动魔法物品的使用魔法装置检定和对抗魔法物品产生的效果时反射豁免检定双投取低。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Magical Klutz [Link]<br>Source Spymaster&#039;s Handbook pg. 7<br>You were born in a place with a plethora of strangely interacting magic, such as Geb, the Mana Wastes, or Nex, and magic is dangerously eager to surge into action around you. You roll twice and take the lower result on Use Magic Device checks to activate items blindly and on Reflex saving throws against effects produced by magic items. </div></div></div><br>谨小慎微（Meticulous）　　［缺陷］：你惯于事先规划好所有细节，而不擅长处理不按计划进行的事件。你在未训练的技能检定承受-2罚值。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input ty